<div class="character-arc text-justify">Meet Layal, our data magician! She's all about bringing data to life with a dash of creativity and a sprinkle of magic. Enjoying animated and superhero movies, Layal's passion shines through in her work as a data scientist and econometrician. Whether she's jazzing up our website or keeping our accounts in check, Layal's got the knack for making things look good and run smoothly.</div>
